{"tid":1833324,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"伊朗國會議員懸賞300萬美元刺殺川普","createTime":"2020-01-21T22:51:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-22T04:11:09.000Z","uid":28765,"like":85,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":83,"replies":[{"pid":"13657ed362b3186defb3d9bbe9f268444cc18a59","tid":1833324,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T22:51:54.000Z","msg":"伊朗國會議員漢澤21日懸賞300萬美元，要給殺死美國總統川普的任何人。(圖取自推特)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.rti.org.tw/assets/thumbnails/2020/01/21/c1aeaaea3a90434aaf5b56f19a4683a6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.rti.org.tw%2Fassets%2Fthumbnails%2F2020%2F01%2F21%2Fc1aeaaea3a90434aaf5b56f19a4683a6.jpg&h=b8c40e2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n伊朗學生通訊社(ISNA)報導，伊朗國會議員漢澤(Ahmad Hamzeh)今天(21日)懸賞300萬美元，要給殺死美國總統川普(Donald Trump)的任何人，以報復美國狙殺伊朗革命衛隊(Iranian Revolutionary Guard)聖城部隊(Quds Force)指揮官蘇雷曼尼(Qassem Soleimani)。<br />\n<br />\n漢澤是伊朗國會(Majlis)知名度不高的議員，他今天代表蘇雷曼尼的家鄉克爾曼(Kerman)發出這項懸賞。<br />\n<br />\n蘇雷曼尼3日在伊拉克巴格達機場(Baghdad airport)遭到美國無人機狙殺，屍體已送回克爾曼安葬。<br />\n<br />\n漢澤是伊朗南部克爾曼省考努季市(Kahnouj)選出的議員，當地位在克爾曼市東南部。<br />\n<br />\n漢澤表示：「任何人殺死川普，我們要給他300萬美元賞金。」<br />\n<br />\n漢澤沒有說明，誰將支付這份賞金。目前距離伊朗國會大選還有1個月。<br />\n<br />\n蘇雷曼尼是最受伊朗人民喜歡的人物。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rti.org.tw/news/view/id/2048959\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rti.org.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2Fid%2F2048959&d=fvWYig%2FFXUG8IHhaG2JvmP%2FZYLwdGiEzwb2OZuYF8yg%3D&h=6d96d7d6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.rti.org.tw/news/view/id/2048959</a>"},{"pid":"ab1500fcb7bef3b04131adf9a46c6e5b8249f117","tid":1833324,"uid":183758,"like":112,"dislike":1,"score":111,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T22:53:51.000Z","msg":"下一個到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1df01ff1d4bb2801b8be612e58b9d4cbdf73264e","tid":1833324,"uid":75050,"like":45,"dislike":2,"score":43,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T22:53:52.000Z","msg":"咁加拿大係唔係又要懸賞